      • setProcessTyp

        void setProcessTyp(java.lang.String processType)
        The processType is simply an information handed in during lean document creation. This information is passed into the item overwrite call back during BOM explosion for to allow the application to determine item details based on this.
        Parameters:
        processType - is a Stirng that simply remembers the processType of the document. No follow up processing is done. null is converted to an empty String.
